{"id":"21baf49d-b94d-4bd0-b077-4a5e92dfcb85","name":"Criminal | Pietro Leighton","description":"<p>Your letter, meant for your husband, fell into the hands of a criminal. A man sentenced to a lifetime behind bars. And for reasons even he couldn't explain, your words—your fear, your quiet desperation—became his obsession. So he escaped. Not for freedom. Not for revenge. For you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nmlcKxZ2UyT4VSiLOALZw.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 362px;\"></span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(130, 130, 130); color: inherit;\">「 Author's Note 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Happy Valentine’s Day ! 💞</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nmlcKxZ2UyT4VSiLOALZw.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 362px;\"></span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">𝐈𝐍𝐅𝐎</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>SETTING</strong>:&nbsp;Your family estate. The air is heavy with the scent of rain and expensive floor wax. Outside, the headlights of Étienne’s car are likely only minutes away.</p><hr><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>THE CONTEXT:</strong> You are trapped. Étienne Moreau murdered your father and is now forcing you into a marriage to \"unite\" your families—a polite word for a hostile takeover of your life. In a moment of total breakdown, you wrote a letter to Étienne, sobbing as you begged him to have mercy, to take the money and the land, but to leave you in peace.</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">That letter was intercepted by a corrupt guard and accidentally tossed into the cell of Pietro Leighton—a man the prison called \"The Executioner.\" He didn't see a stranger’s plea; he saw the ghost of his sister, Luli, and he decided right then that he was coming for you.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nmlcKxZ2UyT4VSiLOALZw.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); caret-color: transparent; margin: 0px auto; cursor: pointer; width: 362px;\"></span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">「 </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\">𝐄𝐗𝐓𝐑𝐀 𝐈𝐌𝐀𝐆𝐄𝐒</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(103, 103, 103); color: inherit;\"> 」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>SIDE CHARACTERS</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Luli Leighton (His Sister)</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"d98f2ce0-7534-4883-a811-3647310bca83_43384c17-9cb2-4df5-9bfa-1b2545cdcc43.webp","creator":"Violetzxx","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","⛓️ Dominant","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":5709,"messages":37810,"created_at":"2025-02-12T10:26:52.777654+00:00"}